				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b24e70c elementor-widget__width-inherit exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="b24e70c" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1600" height="948" src="https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ulta_camp1-scaled-1.webp" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2894" alt="" srcset="https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ulta_camp1-scaled-1.webp 1600w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ulta_camp1-scaled-1-300x178.webp 300w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ulta_camp1-scaled-1-1024x607.webp 1024w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ulta_camp1-scaled-1-768x455.webp 768w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ulta_camp1-scaled-1-1536x910.webp 1536w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ulta_camp1-scaled-1-18x12.webp 18w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ulta_camp1-scaled-1-600x356.webp 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" />															</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-e44f21e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default exad-glass-effect-no wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no wpr-column-slider-no wpr-equal-height-no exad-sticky-section-no" data-id="e44f21e" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-fc3e9f7 exad-glass-effect-no exad-sticky-section-no" data-id="fc3e9f7" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-66583cf exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="66583cf" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">🎓 What is ULTA?</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a720d87 exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="a720d87" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>ULTA is a tuition-free educational program for Ukrainian high school students in grades 9 and 10. Our participants demonstrate a strong passion for technology, active engagement in their communities, proficiency in English, and enthusiasm for learning from MIT mentors. By utilizing MIT’s open education resources, we are a bridge between the rigor of MIT education and the perspectives of Ukrainian students.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
				<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-7bb6237 exad-glass-effect-no exad-sticky-section-no" data-id="7bb6237" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ca63162 exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="ca63162" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">🌍 Our Vision</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-10e4cb4 exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="10e4cb4" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>We envision to empower and inspire the next generation of Ukrainian leaders by sharing world-class knowledge from MIT. These young people are growing up during a time of war and hardship, but they possess a unique perspective that will be invaluable as the country moves forward. Our goal is to equip Ukrainian high-schoolers with the skills, knowledge, and confidence they need to rebuild Ukraine into a thriving, European nation.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2fa7adf elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default exad-glass-effect-no wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no wpr-column-slider-no wpr-equal-height-no exad-sticky-section-no" data-id="2fa7adf" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c60544d exad-glass-effect-no exad-sticky-section-no" data-id="c60544d" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d26e446 exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer" data-id="d26e446" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="spacer.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div class="elementor-spacer">
			<div class="elementor-spacer-inner"></div>
		</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2613f81 exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="2613f81" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">10 student projects for Ukraine</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a857b1d elementor-widget-divider--view-line exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider" data-id="a857b1d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="divider.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div class="elementor-divider">
			<span class="elementor-divider-separator">
						</span>
		</div>
						</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-45b72cc0 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default exad-glass-effect-no wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no wpr-column-slider-no wpr-equal-height-no exad-sticky-section-no" data-id="45b72cc0" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-607f3aad exad-glass-effect-no exad-sticky-section-no" data-id="607f3aad" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1e9c03a2 exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="1e9c03a2" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p><b style="white-space-collapse: preserve;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/khans-300x49.png" alt="" width="214" height="35" /></b></p><p><span style="white-space-collapse: preserve;"><b>Khan Academy f</b></span><b style="white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: inherit;">or Ukraine</b></p><p><span style="white-space-collapse: preserve;">The goal of this collaboration with KSE and Khan Academy is translating Khan Academy into Ukrainian to provide free, world-class education to every Ukrainian student and develop a sustainable economic engine powered by STEM. As of January 2025, Khan Academy for Ukraine raised more than $468,000, and is already serving K-12 Mathematics to Ukrainian high schoolers in need. Please visit the webpage of the initiative for more information: <br /><a href="https://www.khanacademyforukraine.org/">khanacademyforukraine.org</a></span></p>								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
