									<p><b style="white-space-collapse: preserve;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-2858 " src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/aibi-300x127.png" alt="" width="161" height="68" srcset="https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/aibi-300x127.png 300w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/aibi-768x326.png 768w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/aibi-18x8.png 18w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/aibi-600x255.png 600w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/aibi.png 917w" sizes="(max-width: 161px) 100vw, 161px" /></b></p><p><span style="white-space-collapse: preserve;"><b>AIBI</b></span></p><p>AIBI Interviewer is an automated recruitment tool that evaluates candidates using AI interviews, streamlining the hiring process. AIBI is the first of its kind in the Ukrainian job market. AIBI is entirely open-source, enabling adaptation for novel contexts and new use cases in Ukraine. Please see the <a href="https://github.com/yanovsk/ai_interviewer_dashboard_cerebras">GitHub page of the project.</a></p>								</div>
