									<p><b style="white-space-collapse: preserve;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-2849 " src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Captura-de-pantalla-2024-09-27-210632-300x78.png" alt="" width="223" height="58" srcset="https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Captura-de-pantalla-2024-09-27-210632-300x78.png 300w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Captura-de-pantalla-2024-09-27-210632-768x200.png 768w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Captura-de-pantalla-2024-09-27-210632-18x5.png 18w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Captura-de-pantalla-2024-09-27-210632.png 935w" sizes="(max-width: 223px) 100vw, 223px" /></b></p><p><span style="white-space-collapse: preserve;"><b>Ukrainian Reels Generator</b></span></p><p>Ukrainian Reels Generator is an AI-powered agent that can turn any text into a video reel, with AI-generated voiceover, music, and imagery. </p>								</div>
