									<p><b style="white-space-collapse: preserve;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-2867 " src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/stezhkamy-300x52.png" alt="" width="237" height="41" srcset="https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/stezhkamy-300x52.png 300w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/stezhkamy-1024x177.png 1024w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/stezhkamy-768x132.png 768w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/stezhkamy-18x3.png 18w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/stezhkamy-600x103.png 600w, https://ultacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/stezhkamy.png 1137w" sizes="(max-width: 237px) 100vw, 237px" /></b></p><p><span style="white-space-collapse: preserve;"><b>Stezhkamy</b></span></p><p>Stezhkamy is a mobile application that gamifies walking, providing rewards for exploring Ukrainian cities and sights. Ukrainian culture-themed quests, as well as collaboration with local Ukrainian businesses, make it fun to get your steps in every day.</p>								</div>
