					<div id="elementor-tab-content-1541" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="1" role="region" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-1541"><p>Maria was part of the team that worked on RealityCheck, a tool exposing and disarming anti-Ukrainian narratives in real time. She completed ULTA Summer Program I in Barcelona, Spain, and Summer Program II in Warsaw, Poland, both led by MIT mentors. Maria also completed the MIT course &#8220;9.15 The Human Brain,&#8221; taught and proctored by MIT students.</p></div>
