					<div id="elementor-tab-content-3211" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="1" role="region" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-3211"><p>Kateryna was part of the teams behind the Ukrainian Reels Generator, an AI-powered tool for creating video reels, and the Youth Leadership Popularizing Project, which inspires Ukrainian teens by sharing stories of success and perseverance. She completed ULTA Summer Program I in Barcelona, Spain, and Summer Program II in Warsaw, Poland, both led by MIT mentors. Kateryna also completed the MIT course &#8220;14.01 Intro to Economics,&#8221; taught and proctored by MIT students.</p></div>
